list.description: List of fields to be exported from the EDB table, defaults to all if omitted.

string.description: Export Mode

The EDB path to the table being exported, formatted as '.namespace.node.srl.interface'.
StandardOut exports are restricted to its own namespace.
ClusterStandardOut exports can export data from multiple namespaces as well as cluster tables.
Export period, in the format 10s , 1m30s , 1h30m etc.
A where clause to use for the query, e.g. oper-state = down . Enclosing parentheses can be omitted.

list_nested.description: Exports is the list of EDB paths to be exported and mode for each.

single_nested.description: ClusterStandardOutSpec defines the desired state of ClusterStandardOut.
ClusterStandardOutStatus defines the observed state of ClusterStandardOut.

string.description: a comma-separated list of resource fields to fetch/return.  If unspecified, all fields are fetched.  If empty, only key-fields are fetched.
an EQL "where" expression that will be used to filter the set of resources returned.
a label selector string to filter the results based on CR labels
